data.description: You will LOVE this charming cottage, located on 2 lots and owners have already had it surveyed and combined so that you save on the POA dues! The main floor has Master BR & BA (garden tub & separate shower), Living Room with FP (unvented, gas logs), Dining Room, Kitchen with granite counters, black SS appliances (refrigerator, stove, dishwasher, microwave) and Washer & Dryer stay, also. Upstairs you will find two large BRs and BA. Furnished and ready to go for full or part time living or for a rental. It has two HVAC units and everything is almost brand new! It won't last long!
